            <title>[LU-11991] conf-sanity test_32xx fails for separate MGS</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11991</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It is regression after patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/33422&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/33422&lt;/a&gt;&#160;&quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11556&quot; title=&quot;conf-sanity test 32b crashes on MDT umount with &#8220;ASSERTION( atomic_read(&amp;amp;d-&amp;gt;ld_ref) == 0 ) failed: Refcount is 1&#8221;&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-11556&quot;&gt;LU-11556&lt;/a&gt; tests: fix set_persistent_param_and_check breakage&lt;/tt&gt;&quot;.&#160;With separate MGS set_persistent_param_and_check&#160;run at mgs node, but test stop it, and run local MDS+MGS.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
